From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GE-Proton <git@localhost>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 01:20:00 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] winepulse: Retarget DualSense mono output before writes.

The live DualSense mono stream retarget support added in the previous patch
needs to run before controller speaker effect data is submitted. Trigger it
from the render write path when the stream's hotplug generation no longer
matches the current DualSense audio generation.
---
 dlls/winepulse.drv/pulse.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/dlls/winepulse.drv/pulse.c b/dlls/winepulse.drv/pulse.c
--- a/dlls/winepulse.drv/pulse.c
+++ b/dlls/winepulse.drv/pulse.c
@@ -3120,7 +3120,11 @@
         return;
     }
 
+    if (stream->dualsense_mono_registered && stream->haptic_hotplug_generation != g_haptic_hotplug_generation
+            && FAILED(pulse_retarget_dualsense_mono_stream(stream)))
+        return;
+
     bytes = pa_stream_writable_size(stream->stream);
 
     pulse_write_index_catchup(stream);
 
-- 
